title: Can't see the club I started
body:
Wondering if there is a fix going out at some point. The other people in the club have had the tag back for awhile now.

Club: gains Cheat Death
Club Tag: gCD

Thanks for any help!

replies.body:
We're still working on getting some of the clubs issues resolved. In order to assist us, we'll need you to submit a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can individually look at yours.

Let me know if you have any issues with this.
Same problem here! They can still see me as leader. But i cant see the club :(
